Revision history for Alien-gmake

0.21      2018-01-31 10:33:46 -0500
  - implicit modification of PATH is now removed
    (was deprecated in 0.17)

0.20      2017-06-17 11:30:48 -0400
  - Improve probe on Microsoft Windows

0.19      2017-03-23 08:06:47 -0400
  - Remove lingering dependency on Alien::Base::ModuleBuild

0.18      2017-03-22 16:17:11 -0400
  - Migrate to Alien::Build and alienfile

0.17      2017-01-12 22:11:06 -0500
  - implicit modification of PATH is now deprecated
    (see https://metacpan.org/pod/Alien::gmake#CAVEATS for details)

0.16      2017-01-12 16:56:49 -0500
  - production release identical to 0.15_01

0.15_01   2017-01-12 09:48:32 -0500
  - Fix build failure when using MSYS sans Alien::MSYS

0.15      2017-01-11 08:50:02 -0500
  - On Windows (MSWin32), probe for the Gnu Make that comes from
    Alien::MSYS

0.14      2016-02-05 22:57:59 -0500
  - Prune experimental t/run.t test

0.12      2016-01-28 21:21:10 -0500
  - Use Alien::Base::ModuleBuild as configure requires
    instead of Alien::Base

0.11      2015-09-14 05:21:12 -0400
  - Fix for helper, which was incorrectly expecting to be
    called as a class method (eserte++ for reporting GH#1).

0.10      2015-07-13 07:33:41 -0400
  - Update meta to reflect ownership by Alien::Base team

0.09      2015-07-13 07:31:37 -0400
  - Provide %{gmake} helper
  - Require Alien::Base 0.020

0.08      2015-04-22 11:40:06 -0400
  - Require Alien::Base 0.016 (needed for alien_stage_install)

0.07      2015-04-22 11:23:26 -0400
  - use alien_stage_install

0.06      2015-01-23 08:02:18 -0500
  - fix syntax error
  - remove some core libs as explicit prereqs

